-- Homeland Security, Interior Departments Probe Gulf of Mexico Rig Explosion
-- Kim Jordan
-- 2010-04-27T19:53:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-27/homeland-security-interior-departments-probe-gulf-of-mexico-rig-explosion.html

          
          
             The U.S. Interior Department and
Homeland Security are starting a full investigation of the
Deepwater Horizon rig incident in the Gulf of Mexico. U.S.
officials will meet with the executives from BP Plc later today,
according to an e-mailed statement.  
          
          


  


        